    "description": {
      "value": " \n<p><b>Price</b> 4 gp; <b>Weight</b> -</p> \n<p>This is an extra pocket sewn on the inside of a piece of clothing. You gain a +2 <a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/basics-ability-scores/glossary#TOC-Circumstance-Bonus\">circumstance bonus</a> on <a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/skills/sleight-of-hand\">Sleight of Hand</a> checks to conceal an item in an inside pocket. Detecting the compartment requires a successful DC 15 <a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/skills/perception\">Perception</a> check at minimum (DC 20 if empty), even if you aren't trained in <a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/skills/sleight-of-hand\">Sleight of Hand</a>.</p> \n<p>The inside pocket is 1 inch deep. Different styles open from the top or from the side, and some have button flaps to secure the contents.</p> \n",
